@startuml
title Forecast Comparison Flow

actor Farmer
participant "Web Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "Forecast Service" as Forecast
participant "Weather Feed" as Weather
participant "Satellite Feed" as Satellite
participant "Scenario Engine" as Scenario
database "PostGIS" as PostGIS

Farmer -> Dashboard : open field forecast page
Dashboard -> Forecast : request selected days
Forecast -> Weather : load weather windows
Forecast -> Satellite : load image windows
Forecast -> PostGIS : load parcel and crop metadata
Forecast -> Scenario : compare requested days
Scenario -> Scenario : produce water need and stress bands
Scenario -> Forecast : return day-by-day comparison
Forecast -> Dashboard : show green/yellow/red timeline

@enduml